The B2B2C Promo Decoupling process runs Thursday every week. It is executed via a Snowflake Task (COL_DB.COL_DM.B2B2C_PROMO_DECOUPLING). 

The promo decoupling process analyses the promotional income earned across all B2B2C (matched) transactions for a given promo week (Wednesday - Tuesday). It sums all deal income, grouped by store ID, supplier, SKU and other attributes. 

